Requirements:

OCaml (>= 3.11) with unix support
Linux (not tested on other platforms)
ocp-build (>= 1.99)
gcc (not tested with other compilers)

Commands:

In the root of the directory:

$ ocp-build -init
$ ocp-build configure
$ ocp-build build
$ ocp-build install

You need to be admin for the install part, you can specify a local folder during the configure step.
